-- Private equity to sell 50 pct stake in African insurer Continental Re
-- By Chijioke Ohuocha
-- Wed Jul 16, 2014 08:58AM EDT
-- None



LAGOS, July 16 (Reuters) - Private equity firm Emerging Capital Partners plans to sell its 50.6 percent stake in Continental Reinsurance <CONTINS.LG>, the African insurer said in a filing with the Nigerian Stock Exchange.

